snippet.title: Rusty Rivets Botasaur Dinosaur Spin Master Toy Unboxing Review || Keith's Toy Box
snippet.description:

We love this RC toys unboxing, because of all of our RC trucks, this RC4WD Hero is the most RC scale truck we own so far.

snippet.title: Hand Controlled Flying Saucer UFO w IR and LED Lights - Unboxing Demo Review
snippet.description:
It's so easy to fly this Hand-Controlled Flying Saucer UFO with Infrared (IR) and LED Lights!  Just wave your hand under it to make it fly, no need for a remote control!  It works by infrared (IR) technology that detects any surface below it and makes it hover and rise up!  It has a foam body that lets it withstand falls, crashes, or bounce of walls!  Its flashing LED lights makes it really COOL to fly at night! Other than just your hand, you can also try more advanced tricks like using your legs, knees, arms or shoulders!  Use the catching stick to play catch with friends and toss it back and forth!    Similar to Vectron Wave or Air Hogs or Air Eagle UFO Flyers
- Easy-to-fly hand-controlled Flying Saucer, UFO, perfect for beginners, no need for remote control
- Works by Infrared (IR) technology that detects any surface and makes it hover and rise up!
- Foam body lets it withstand falls and crashes, or lets it bounce of walls!
- Flashing LED lights make it really cool to fly at night!
- Other than your hand, you can also use your legs, knees, arms or shoulders!
- Play catch with friends and toss it back and forth with the use of the catching stick!
- Comes with USB charging cable and built-in rechargeable lithium batteries, charge for 20 minutes, good for 3-7 minutes of flying time.
- Fly indoors or outdoors, but keep away from people's faces, eyes, animals, and fragile objects.

snippet.title: Vtech Smart Shots Sports Center Unboxing - Toddlers Learning and Playing Sports Toys
snippet.description:
Unboxing Smart Shots Sports Center! Toddler play and learn with sports toys, basketball and soccer action!

Nessa is a natural she takes over and starts slamming the basketball in the basket, I see a lot of promise for this one year old in her sports skills.

Nate gets all excited about unboxing the toy set, he has seen so many youtube unboxing toys videos that for him to experience it in real life really is something for him.  

We all start testing out this playset and throwing the basketball and soccer ball trying to make shot, our sports skills are rusty but it was still good family fun testing out this toy. 

The interactive learning part of the set is great, there are all type of knobs and buttons for the kids to explore and learn their numbers and ABCs while playing.  

The set was really easy to put together, came right out of the box.  Only technical part was using a screwdriver to open the batter box but that was really easy.

Overall this is a great kids toy for toddlers, as it is aimed to that age group for learning and playing.  We love Vtech toys and have lots of different sets even before making any videos, so they are very popular toys.

What is your favorite movie?
I love the Minions from the Minion movie but my favorite movies are superhero movies. I love Batman, Robin, Superman, the Avengers, Hulk, Iron Man, Spiderman, Captain America, Wolverine and Thor. 90° rotatable camera allow your kids to take pictures and selfie with one camera, just adjust the angle, easy for kids to take photos.

Built-in 4 funny and mini games(Whac-A-Mole, Ninja Run Online, Welcome the God of Wealth, Brave Money) in this smart watch, children can play through the touch screen and select the game for their prefer, train them in coordination and thinking in leisure time.
